Owesifazane oneminyaka engu-53, (igama lakhe elingatholakalanga), kuthiwa ubesegunjini lokulala ngesikhathi kuqubuka umlilo okukholakala ukuthi ususwe yisiphefu ebesikhanyiswe ngoba kuhambe ugesi. Okhulumela inkampani yonogada iReaction Unit of South Africa, uMnuz Pram Balram, uthe ngesikhathi kufika ithimba lonogada benkampani endaweni yesehlakalo, lithole indodana kamufi ebalandise ngokwenzekile. “Sifice owesilisa oneminyaka engu-34 othe uyindodana kamufi. Uthe ubelele kwelinye igumbi ngesikhathi ezwa unina ekhala ecela usizo. Ngesikhathi ephuma uthe ubone ingxenye yomuzi wakubo igqamuka amalangabi,” kusho uBalram. Uthe indodana kamufi itshele onogada ukuthi izamile ukutakula unina kodwa yehluleka ngenxa yamalangabi nentuthu ebisivimbanisile. Kuthiwa indodana kamufi ihangulwe wumlilo ezingalweni ngesikhathi izama ukusiza unina obesesithele efwini lentuthu namalangabi omlilo. Okhulumela amaphoyisa KwaZulu-Natal, uCaptain Nqobile Gwala, uthe kuphenywa imbangela yokufa komuntu esiteshini samaphoyisa eVerulam.